{"tid":2418601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"721白衣人暴動開審　扯貓尾　法官「不知情」批評警方做咗啲乜嘢","createTime":"2021-02-22T17:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T23:41:55.000Z","uid":261647,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c2381a42749d759e6ecc91be991b703040e2a8f1","tid":2418601,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T17:44:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100most/posts/3617477641713190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100most%2Fposts%2F3617477641713190&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=19bd9154\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100most/posts/3617477641713190</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2YZRUoT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2YZRUoT.jpg&h=6a0c2195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：100毛<br />\n<br />\n721元朗恐襲發生至今已經年半，當中少數有被落案控告嘅白衣人，案件今日喺區域法院開審。<br />\n<br />\n喺庭上，法官多次批評控方辦事手法，包括警員編號、人名、數字出錯；遲交案情修訂；辯方未簽署承認事實，但控方推說話「簽緊」；而喺庭上亦有披露，警方事隔年半先知收錯受害人醫療報告，被法官批評警方將報告「放入雪櫃、雪咗年幾」，質疑佢哋呢年半「做咗啲乜嘢」⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n案件中八名被告，其中兩人今日承認暴動罪。提提大家，噚日係721元朗恐襲19個月，當日一大班攞住架生、大搖大擺喺元朗站內外襲擊市民嘅白衣人，到而家只有八人被落案檢控。"},{"pid":"331231041b3c4c0e32f0b7459057bdd2263b518d","tid":2418601,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2381a42749d759e6ecc91be991b703040e2a8f1","tid":2418601,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T17:44:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100most/posts/3617477641713190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100most%2Fposts%2F3617477641713190&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=19bd9154\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100most/posts/3617477641713190</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2YZRUoT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2YZRUoT.jpg&h=6a0c2195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：100毛<br />\